    <item>
      <title>业界称，即使可可价格飙升，亚洲的巧克力爱好者仍会大吃一惊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-09/chocolate-lovers-in-asia-will-indulge-even-as-cocoa-prices-soar-industry-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位业内资深人士表示，尽管可可价格飙升至 20 世纪 70 年代以来的最高水平，但亚洲越来越多的巧克力爱好者仍会沉迷于甜食。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-09/chocolate-lovers-in-asia-will-indulge-even-as-cocoa-prices-soar-industry-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
